  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the lamb to the skillet and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the breadcrumbs to the skillet and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chopped parsley, mint, lemon juice, salt, black pepper, and paprika to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Continue cooking for an additional 2 minutes, stirring frequently.",
    "Serve the lamb stir-fry hot, garnished with additional parsley and mint if desired."
